# AI Traffic Blockage Prediction & Smart Route Recommendation System

note: this app will be used only in Rabat Morocco for the time being.

Goal: build a system that:

1- Predicts potential traffic blockages or congestion;

2- Suggests alternative routes;

3- Estimates travel time.



Steps:


1- make a simple app that gives the shortest route based on the user's current location (or a choosen location) and the destination.
tools: Leaflet/Folium to create interactive maps,ipstack.com api to get the user's location, NetworkX for graph and algorithm A*, streamlit for frontend. (Done)

